{"tid":361662,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"恒指新貴 萬洲","createTime":"2017-08-16T10:11:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T11:29:56.000Z","uid":45440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"53a72e8030b4630437a7cd8087ae73cd635e16a0","tid":361662,"uid":45440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T10:11:29.000Z","msg":"2017 年 8 月 16 日<br />\n恒生指數有限公司宣佈指數檢討結果<br />\n恒生指數有限公司 (「恒生指數公司」) 今天宣佈，截至 2017 年 6 月 30 日之恒<br />\n生指數系列季度檢討結果，所有變更將於 2017 年 9 月 4 日 (星期一) 起生效。<br />\n1. 恒生指數<br />\n恒生指數成份股將有以下的變動，成份股數目由 49 隻增加至 50 隻。<br />\n加入：<br />\n代號 公司 流通系數 (%) 分類指數<br />\n288 萬洲國際有限公司 65 工商業<br />\n有關成份股名單，請參閱附件一。"},{"pid":"d758bf32e72b6c2d9c52da63f61ef3d2bc925a13","tid":361662,"uid":45440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T10:12:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hsi.com.hk/HSI-Net/static/revamp/contents/zh_hk/news/pressRelease/20170816c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hsi.com.hk%2FHSI-Net%2Fstatic%2Frevamp%2Fcontents%2Fzh_hk%2Fnews%2FpressRelease%2F20170816c.pdf&d=wUgEeUynGuOXmQDGHl7haTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=56910f3b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hsi.com.hk/HSI-Net/static/revamp/contents/zh_hk/news/pressRelease/20170816c.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"c259a60df6443c0f1786163d37dd3b435168d140","tid":361662,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T10:13:41.000Z","msg":"豬肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2382沒有了"},{"pid":"11e42fc39893a4f76348b6419c7bdd66fa172189","tid":361662,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T10:14:15.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b10ea7f192cd9c205b42695629f33901a9f6f1","tid":361662,"uid":45440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T10:15:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>豬肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2382沒有了<